- This examples help you to open up a new alloy window on a button click.
- It also, lets you know how to pass arguments between windows.
- You will undersatnd how to update the label when you receieve data from another winodw.
- Also helps you to understand how to hide/show a label.

- Look into screenshots folder for the project screen shorts.
- You can find more about this project at - http://tialloy.blogspot.com/2013/10/opening-new-window-in-alloy-using.html
- You can find more examples at following blog. - http://tialloy.blogspot.com/
